{"tid":2262093,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】2019號熱帶氣旋 天鵝 GONI（22W）","createTime":"2020-10-28T22:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T07:01:14.000Z","uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"de3f1c730a50fad6137198957d76e8c0bb5caae3","tid":2262093,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 天鵝</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"x-large\">2019號熱帶氣旋 天鵝 GONI（22W）</span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">來源：南韓<br />\n意義：一種體積大而優雅，羽毛通常呈白色，頸部瘦而長的雀鳥，生活在河流或湖泊上。冬天的時候由西伯利亞飛往韓國生活。象徵忠誠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。 <br />\n為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。 <br />\n請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。 <br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">部份手機於使用app版時可能無法載入以下圖片，暫時需要按入圖片並選擇在瀏覽器開啟或使用web版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_2026.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_2026.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_2026.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/2019-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/2019-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/2019-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/202022W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/GONI.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"},{"pid":"61b1022139bba53fb2a73ddadffc6169821a7d52","tid":2262093,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:29:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\"><ins>◤颱風追擊必備資訊</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n◆ 香港天文台 (HKO)：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Finformtc%2FtcSmap_uc.htm&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=3a0976d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 日本氣象廳 (JMA)：<a href=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2dac7e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh</a><br />\n◆ 中央氣象台 (CMA)：<a href=\"http://www.nmc.gov.cn/publish/typhoon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmc.gov.cn%2Fpublish%2Ftyphoon&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f739d0df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmc.gov.cn/publish/typhoon</a><br />\n◆ 中央氣象局 (CWB)：<a href=\"http://www.cwb.gov.tw/V7/prevent/typhoon/ty.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cwb.gov.tw%2FV7%2Fprevent%2Ftyphoon%2Fty.htm&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=a08b7c6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cwb.gov.tw/V7/prevent/typhoon/ty.htm</a><br />\n◆ 韓國氣象廳 (KMA)：<a href=\"http://web.kma.go.kr/chn/weather/typoon/typhoon.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.kma.go.kr%2Fchn%2Fweather%2Ftypoon%2Ftyphoon.jsp&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=d6f2fc88\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.kma.go.kr/chn/weather/typoon/typhoon.jsp</a><br />\n◆ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC)：<a href=\"http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.usno.navy.mil%2FJTWC&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=e724dec8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC</a><br />\n◆ 美國海軍實驗中心 (NRL)：<a href=\"http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/TC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nrlmry.navy.mil%2FTC.html&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=1a567b59\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nrlmry.navy.mil/TC.html</a><br />\n<br />\n◇ 認識熱帶氣旋：<a href=\"http://j.mp/tc_edu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2Ftc_edu&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=b8e80266\" target=\"_blank\">http://j.mp/tc_edu</a><br />\n◇ 熱帶氣旋實時資料：<a href=\"http://j.mp/tc_realtime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2Ftc_realtime&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=dff9df13\" target=\"_blank\">http://j.mp/tc_realtime</a><br />\n◇ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KipuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=cf33fdf9\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2AnFp4H\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2WnV1h8\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"https://bit.ly/2LltW7T\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pNBL9q\" /> <br />\n▲ 水汽圖<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" /> <br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>渦度、風切、輻合輻散及駛流圖的圖片因初學者較難理解已收起，以節省空間及減少讀取之數據量，欲查閲者請自行打開</strong></span></span><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nmxoSz\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pn2N10\" /> <br />\n▲ 渦度<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nHiMVb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/oJKmvW\" /> <br />\n▲ 垂直風切變<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/od23Nx\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pkPCsA\" /> <br />\n▲ 高空輻散<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/ndaL81\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/noFlPK\" /> <br />\n▲ 低層輻合<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qjDsUy\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/o4Jzi5\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nUmvwF\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/od7LAQ\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/q73CZx\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/r3N8cc\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/ohj5iY\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nZajhj\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qOjq3w\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/nnWrjt\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/rcX7BC\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/p388ZC\" /> <br />\n▲ 駛流圖 (請按照熱帶氣旋的氣壓參考) </blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/o1uJVb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/qItfkL\" /> <br />\n▲ 浪高／浪向<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/dmH6HF\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/cA53Zd\" /> <br />\n▲ 海水溫度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2ouh1JP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2ouh1JP.png&h=42d7d586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶氣旋會怎麼走？</strong>"},{"pid":"9140131d13521d90e2bc50b7eb0b0140917e2eb9","tid":2262093,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:30:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://m.weather.gov.hk/image/radar_scale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weather.gov.hk%2Fimage%2Fradar_scale.jpg&h=087d95fd&s={SIZE}\" />　　<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_256_320/rad256_6.jpg\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_128_320/rad128_6.jpg\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://pda.weather.gov.hk/radar/rad_064_320/rad064_6.jpg\" /><br />\n▲ 香港256／128／64公里雷達<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qQj8Xe\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qqyU9G\" /><br />\n▲ 實時天氣照片<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qPKaOw\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2qu5ZAb\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rdU6AS\" /><br />\n▲ 本港分區氣溫／濕度／能見度<br />\n<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2pSLUlJ\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2rqtOIV\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2sLVc4U\" /><br />\n▲ 本港風向及風速／最高陣風／海平面氣壓</strong>"},{"pid":"2e3afa5998af4dfec7b5d840ec0563b38e8a07a1","tid":2262093,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png&h=fae8adfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png&h=60556b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png&h=85440aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png&h=27f79c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGW（gale warning)－由日本氣象廳發出，意思係24小時內會有熱帶風暴形成，即係估計24小時內命名<br />\nTCFA （tropical cyclone formation alert）－由JTWC發出，指24小時會有熱帶氣旋（包括熱帶低氣壓）生成，即24小時內正式編號升格<br />\nFFS－美國全球預報系統(GFS)的俗稱，諷刺其計算結果如同FF，近年預報準確度有所提升<br />\nCPA TO HK－該風暴與本港之最接近距離<br />\nJTWC BIN C之旅-收集每報JTWC預報報文中的CPA TO HK，事後可以實際CPA TO HK對照作BIN C之用<br />\n馮瑞權－澳門氣象局前局長<br />\n風水權－馮瑞權俗稱<br />\nCCM－天文台新任台長鄭楚明簡稱<br />\n赤的疑惑－高登氣象台台長，連登CDROM<br />\n七長官/7長官-製作氣象台警報gif會員<br />\nRose－製作高登風格天氣警告圖的會員，其作品並不授予連登使用<br />\n楊振權副庭長－Baroclinic於高登的最新名字<br />\n桜の抹茶刺身－連登氣象post負責人1<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶－連登氣象post負責人2<br />\n雪菜肉絲炆米－連登颱風航空交通post負責人<br />\n一個地球人－連登中仔細分析颱風走向及其他高空氣象圖的高質會員，近一年較少上水<br />\n當榴蓮遇上芒果(已更名)－連登中另一位氣象知識豐富的高質會員<br />\n逝去的不回來/夏天冬天夏天－知名假膠attention seeker<br />\n南珠隻狗－連登中氣象知識亦較豐富的會員<br />\n伊甸園菜肉餃－伊甸園市長在連登的最新名字<br />\nXXXXXX堅豎－土豆在連登的分身，近一年較少上水<br />\nDH-direct hit 本港一百公里內掠過<br />\n中出－風暴中心直接橫過本港<br />\n貓5－cat5 五級颱風的英文簡稱<br />\n五隻貓－同上，有cat1-5<br />\n醉警－酷熱天氣警告誤字<br />\n南海之王－氣象迷對香港天文台的尊稱，指其對南海熱帶氣旋預測表現良好，但只限接近廣東沿岸的南海部份，因此又被稱為南海北部之王<br />\nSTNR－滯留不動<br />\nN0.1－向北移0.1度，/E/S/W（東/南/西）同理<br />\n8中X－天文台指定8個測風站中有X個達標<br />\nlogin－登陸，源於cctvb錯將&Prime;登陸&Prime;打成&Prime;登錄&Prime;<br />\nlogin password－由上引申之術語，意指登陸地<br />\n0號觀望訊號－香港傳媒於熱帶氣旋仍末形成時，已大肆吹奏香港會打風；又或熱帶氣旋已形成，但並非採取接近本港之路徑，傳媒卻仍吹奏有機會打風。此詞用於諷刺傳媒猶如代替天文台發出熱帶氣旋警告訊號<br />\n(香港)暴雨走廊－指大嶼山東北起，經荃青葵，擴展至沙田大埔一段，因西南水汽易受此一帶地型抬升影響較易有暴雨。靈感來自美國「龍捲風走廊」。以下為經典例子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=33884fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e80d38ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為一分鐘風速標準，轉化至十分鐘標準（hko,jma標準）請乘0.93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nchanho.jpg－副檔名可以改為任意三個不同英文字，為伊甸園市長愛用圖片，即下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1ebcd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為兩登氣象台提及峴港時愛用cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5d8a07b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在洲－「在維多利亞港內的青洲」，天文台以海拔較高且位於廣義維港邊緣的青洲暗示港內達烈風，為天文台搬龍門的代表例子"},{"pid":"f6377093bccf090a18cc0a3ba3d0c3e5090ff9c4","tid":2262093,"uid":321194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:35:58.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daabdebbe9b8abcfefd7e94ec7cc5e6a77da05b6","tid":2262093,"uid":143343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8441fcfb77e6c3bc8edebef73ba350b3ea6c3aa3","tid":2262093,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:37:02.000Z","msg":"仲有冇機會八號"},{"pid":"00fdededc96b434bf3844f23a50d179efed7b7f1","tid":2262093,"uid":15480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:39:07.000Z","msg":"個個風都去海南島既"},{"pid":"ab1cbb1deead7bf1ed16e0d93c96e0e16d0ff7a9","tid":2262093,"uid":11067,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T22:41:44.000Z","msg":"今個post實hit 過上個post好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad9298319bfecae1cd16e3c3276be059c043869","tid":2262093,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0